description:
Math worksheets with consistent cultural characters (Anansi, Raven, Coyote) using Nano Banana for classroom use by teachers.

Character Worksheets leverages Gemini 2.5 Flash Image's character consistency and multi-turn editing capabilities to solve a critical problem in educational content creation. Teachers need multicultural worksheets featuring traditional characters like Anansi, Raven, and Coyote, but existing AI tools generate visually inconsistent characters across problems, breaking narrative coherence and confusing students.

Our application demonstrates three core Nano Banana features:
(1) Character Consistency - the same cultural character appears identically across multiple math problems;
(2) Multi-turn Editing - teachers can customize characters ("add teacher clothes") while preserving their cultural identity;
(3) Contextual Scene Generation - placing consistent characters in different educational scenarios while maintaining their appearance.
